===Pronunciation 1===
*{{IPA|ﾋ坼aﾉｪndﾉ嘲} (US)

====Adjective====
'''hinder'''
# Of or belonging to that part or end which is in the rear, or which follows; as, the hinder part of a wagon; the hinder parts of a horse.

===Pronunciation 2===
*{{IPA|ﾋ坼ﾉｪndﾉ嘲} (US)

====Verb====
'''hinder'''
#To cause someone to be behind.
#To make it difficult for someone or something to do something.

